	Applicants who are not invited for an interview within 8 weeks may consider their applications unsuccessful.', '', 'https://jobs.ctgoodjobs.hk/job/10180207/quantity-surveyor?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'google_jobs_CTgoodjobs.hk', '5 days ago', '', 0, 'experienced', '2026-07-15 00:10:18', '2026-07-15 00:10:18', 0, NULL, 0);
