I possess the Construction Industry Safety Card (Green Card) and am proficient in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin, which will facilitate clear communication with field teams and stakeholders. My technical skills include AutoCAD, Revit, Navisworks, and BIM coordination, as well as data analysis tools such as Excel, VBA, and Power BI. I am familiar with HKIS practice notes, relevant Hong Kong ordinances, and local surveying conventions, and I am eager to apply this knowledge to land surveying tasks including geodetic, boundary, topographic, and photogrammetric surveys.

