ination. Fluent in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin. Holds a Green Card and is a Student Member of HKIS and RICS. Completed a summer internship at Rider Levett Bucknall (RLB) assisting senior QS team, and a part-time student assistant role at PolyU. Seeking a challenging role in building surveying to apply analytical and problem-solving skills.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

