I understand that the role requires independence and responsiveness in a dynamic housing environment. My Cantonese fluency, coupled with strong communication skills in English and Mandarin, enables me to liaise effectively with residents, contractors, and colleagues. I am also proficient in MS Project and Excel, which I have used to support project scheduling and data analysis during my part-time role as a student assistant at PolyU’s Building and Real Estate Department.

I am drawn to the Hong Kong Housing Society’s reputation for delivering high-quality public housing and innovative community projects. I am confident that my technical skills, local knowledge, and dedication to professional growth will allow me to make a meaningful contribution to your team.

Thank you for considering my application. I look forward to the opportunity to discuss how I can support the Housing Society’s objectives.

