 analysis tools (Python, Power BI). Holder of Green Card (Construction Industry Safety Card) and HKIS Student Member, eligible for HKIS APC pathway. Fluent in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin. Seeking a QS Assistant role to apply technical skills and contribute to project success in a dynamic engineering firm.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

