nt, cost estimation, tender documentation, and contract administration. Proficient in AutoCAD, Revit, CostX, Navisworks, Bluebeam, MS Project, Excel, VBA, SPSS, Python, and Power BI. Holder of Construction Industry Safety Card (Green Card) and Revit Architecture Certified Professional. Fluent in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin. Active HKIS and RICS Student Member, eligible for HKIS APC pathway. Seeking a Graduate Quantity Surveyor role at Arcadis to apply technical skills and contribute to sustainable projects.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

