h, and Mandarin. Holder of Green Card and HKIS/RICS Student Memberships. Seeking a Graduate Quantity Surveyor role at Chun Wo Development Holdings to apply my technical skills and contribute to contract administration, subcontractor measurement, and cost control on HK construction projects.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

