As a PolyU Surveying graduate, I am eligible for the HKIS APC graduate pathway, and I am already an HKIS Student Member. This pathway reflects my commitment to professional development and my familiarity with HKIS standards, relevant Hong Kong ordinances, and local surveying practices. I am confident that my trilingual fluency in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin will enable seamless communication with colleagues, subcontractors, and clients across Chun Wo’s diverse project teams.

Chun Wo’s reputation for delivering complex civil engineering and building projects in Hong Kong is well known, and I am particularly drawn to the opportunity to contribute to contract administration, subcontractor measurement, and cost comparison tasks. My experience with VBA, Power BI, and Python also allows me to bring data-driven efficiencies to reporting and analysis.

