IS Student Member, eligible for the HKIS APC pathway. Fluent in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin. Seeking a Graduate Quantity Surveyor position at Shui On Building Contractors to apply technical skills and develop expertise in site-based QS services, measurement, and contract administration.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

