with diverse stakeholders. Holder of Green Card and active HKIS/RICS Student Member, committed to pursuing professional qualification. Eager to apply my skills and learn in foundation and civil engineering projects at Kin Wing Engineering, contributing to accurate cost management and project success.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

