ure Certified Professional. Fluent in Cantonese, English, and Mandarin. HKIS and RICS Student Member, eligible for HKIS APC pathway. Seeking to apply strong analytical and technical skills to support Wing Ho Yuen Landscaping Co., Ltd. in delivering accurate cost management and contract administration for landscaping projects.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

