coordination skills on building, A&A, and facade projects in Hong Kong.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

I am writing to express my strong interest in the (Assistant) Quantity Surveyor position at your firm, as advertised through RecruitPRO Consultancy Hong Kong Limited. As a recent BSc (Hons) in Surveying graduate from The Hong Kong Polytechnic University, I am eager to contribute to your team while advancing my professional development in Hong Kong’s dynamic construction sector.

