As a PolyU Surveying graduate and current HKIS Student Member, I am eligible for the HKIS APC graduate pathway, and I am committed to pursuing professional qualification under the HKIS framework. My academic training and internship experience have given me a strong understanding of Hong Kong’s surveying practices, including familiarity with relevant ordinances and the importance of accurate cost control in ASD, building, A&A, and façade projects.

I understand your firm is a leading sub-contractor with a reputation for delivering high-quality building projects in Hong Kong. I am confident that my technical skills, trilingual proficiency (Cantonese, English, Mandarin), and proactive attitude would allow me to support your team effectively. While I have approximately six months of related experience, I am prepared to work diligently to bridge any gaps and contribute meaningfully from day one.

