[Your Name]', '["How familiar are you with the HKIS APC requirements for the QS division, and what steps have you taken to prepare for the APC?", "Can you describe your experience with the Hong Kong Standard Method of Measurement (SMM) and how you applied it during your internship at RLB?", "This role involves projects for ASD, building, A&A, and facade. Have you worked on any similar projects, and what challenges do you anticipate in cost management for A&A works?", "What is your understanding of the Building (Planning) Regulations in Hong Kong, and how do they impact quantity surveying practices?", "Describe a time when you had to resolve a discrepancy in measurements or costs with a contractor or colleague. How did you handle it?"]', '2026-07-21 14:47:06', NULL, NULL);
