 analytical and software skills in a land surveying role, with a keen interest in BIM-based asset management and smart infrastructure. Eager to contribute to Meinhardt''s geospatial and land survey services team.', 'Dear Hiring Manager,

I am writing to express my strong interest in the Assistant Land Surveyor position (Ref: 70526) at Meinhardt Consulting Engineers. As a final-year BSc (Hons) in Surveying student at The Hong Kong Polytechnic University, I have long admired Meinhardt’s reputation for delivering technically robust, cost-effective solutions across Hong Kong’s major infrastructure and building projects. Your firm’s integrated approach—spanning geospatial services, BIM, and smart infrastructure—aligns closely with my academic training and practical experience.

