As a PolyU Surveying graduate, I am eligible for the HKIS APC graduate pathway, and I am already an HKIS Student Member. This ensures I am familiar with the professional standards and ethical practices upheld by the Hong Kong surveying community. I also hold a valid Construction Industry Safety Card (Green Card) and have completed a CIC-accredited BIM Basic Modelling Course, which aligns with the Department’s increasing reliance on digital spatial data and BIM coordination.

